description: This top 10% Gaston purrs with a rating of 52, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 156, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, 2 for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
